    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a bard, you gain the following class features.</p><h3>Hit Points</h3><p><strong>Hit Dice:</strong> 1d8 per bard level<br /><strong>Hit Points at 1st Level:</strong> 8 + your Constitution modifier<br /><strong>Hit Points at Higher Levels:</strong> 1d8 (or 5) + your Constitution modifier per bard level after 1st</p><h3>Proficiencies</h3><p><strong>Armor:</strong> Light armor<br /><strong>Weapons:</strong> Simple weapons, hand crossbows, longswords, rapiers, shortswords<br /><strong>Tools:</strong> Three musical instruments of your choice<br /><strong>Saving Throws:</strong> Dexterity, Charisma<br /><strong>Skills:</strong> Choose any three</p><h3>Equipment</h3><p>You start with the following equipment, in addition to the equipment granted by your background:</p><ul><li>(a) a rapier, (b) a longsword, or (c) any simple weapon</li><li>(a) a diplomat's pack or (b) an entertainer's pack</li><li>(a) a lute or (b) any other musical instrument</li><li>Leather armor and a dagger</li></ul><h1>Bard Advancement</h1><table border=\"0\"><thead><tr><td>Level</td><td>Proficiency Bonus</td><td>Features</td></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1st</td><td>+2</td><td>@Compendium[mka.classfeatures.u4NLajXETJhJU31v]{Spellcasting}, @Compendium[mka.classfeatures.hpLNiGq7y67d2EHA]{Bardic Inspiration (d6)}</td></tr><tr><td>2nd</td><td>+2</td><td>@Compendium[mka.classfeatures.ezWijmCnlnQ9ZRX2]{Jack of All Trades}, @Compendium[mka.classfeatures.he8RpPXwSl2lVSIk]{Song of Rest (d6)}</td></tr><tr><td>3rd</td><td>+2</td><td>@Compendium[mka.classfeatures.ILhzFHiRrqgQ9dFJ]{Bard College} @Compendium[mka.classfeatures.aQLg7BWdRnm4Hr9S]{Expertise}</td></tr><tr><td>4th</td><td>+2</td><td>@Compendium[mka.classfeatures.s0Cc2zcX0JzIgam5]{Ability Score Improvement}</td></tr><tr><td>5th</td><td>+3</td><td>@Compendium[mka.classfeatures.hpLNiGq7y67d2EHA]{Bardic Inspiration (d8)}, @Compendium[mka.classfeatures.3VDZGs5Ug3hIE322]{Font of Inspiration}</td></tr><tr><td>6th</td><td>+3</td><td>@Compendium[mka.classfeatures.SEJmsjkEhdAZ90ki]{Countercharm}, Bard College feature</td></tr><tr><td>7th</td><td>+3</td><td>4th Level Spell Slot</td></tr><tr><td>8th</td><td>+3</td><td>@Compendium[mka.classfeatures.s0Cc2zcX0JzIgam5]{Ability Score Improvement}</td></tr><tr><td>9th</td><td>+4</td><td>5th Level Spell Slot @Compendium[mka.classfeatures.he8RpPXwSl2lVSIk]{Song of Rest (d8)}</td></tr><tr><td>10th</td><td>+4</td><td>@Compendium[mka.classfeatures.hpLNiGq7y67d2EHA]{Bardic Inspiration (d10)}, @Compendium[mka.classfeatures.aQLg7BWdRnm4Hr9S]{Expertise}, @Compendium[mka.classfeatures.aonJ2YjkqkYB9WYB]{Magical Secrets}</td></tr><tr><td>11th</td><td>+4</td><td>6th Level Spell Slot</td></tr><tr><td>12th</td><td>+4</td><td>@Compendium[mka.classfeatures.s0Cc2zcX0JzIgam5]{Ability Score Improvement}</td></tr><tr><td>13th</td><td>+5</td><td>7th Level Spell Slot, @Compendium[mka.classfeatures.he8RpPXwSl2lVSIk]{Song of Rest (d10)}</td></tr><tr><td>14th</td><td>+5</td><td>@Compendium[mka.classfeatures.aonJ2YjkqkYB9WYB]{Magical Secrets}, Bard College feature</td></tr><tr><td>15th</td><td>+5</td><td>8th Level Spell Slot, @Compendium[mka.classfeatures.hpLNiGq7y67d2EHA]{Bardic Inspiration (d12)}</td></tr><tr><td>16th</td><td>+5</td><td>@Compendium[mka.classfeatures.s0Cc2zcX0JzIgam5]{Ability Score Improvement}</td></tr><tr><td>17th</td><td>+6</td><td>9th Level Spell Slot, @Compendium[mka.classfeatures.he8RpPXwSl2lVSIk]{Song of Rest (d12)}</td></tr><tr><td>18th</td><td>+6</td><td>@Compendium[mka.classfeatures.aonJ2YjkqkYB9WYB]{Magical Secrets}</td></tr><tr><td>19th</td><td>+6</td><td>@Compendium[mka.classfeatures.s0Cc2zcX0JzIgam5]{Ability Score Improvement}</td></tr><tr><td>20th</td><td>+6</td><td>@Compendium[mka.classfeatures.GBYN5rH4nh1ocRlY]{Superior Inspiration}</td></tr></tbody></table><h1>Bard Colleges</h1><p>@Compendium[mka.subclasses.MNvsEc4D2ccX7dQT]{College of Lore}</p>",
